# Stack conventions

- **Next.js App Router** + TypeScript
- **Prisma 7** + **PostgreSQL** via `@prisma/adapter-pg` + `pg` (`lib/db.ts`)
- Generated client: `lib/generated/prisma` (gitignored; `prisma generate` / postinstall)
- **Production:** `https://presentpo.com` — Cloudflare DNS → always-on host (see `docs/deploy-presentpo.md`)
- Local DB: `docker compose up -d db` with URL in `.env.example`
- Domain logic in `lib/`; API under `app/api/`
- Env: `DATABASE_URL`, `TEACHER_PASSWORD` (`TEACHER_PIN` fallback), `PUBLIC_APP_URL`, `EARLY_CHECKIN_MINUTES`, `TZ`
- No SQLite `file:` URLs

